CTR-SDK Development Tool - make_banner - Generates ICN/BNR files
Version: 1.0

2013 (c) 3DSGuy

/******** Downloads ********/

Windows (32-Bit): https://dl.dropbox.com/u/60710927/CTR/make_banner/make_banner_1.0_windows.7z

Linux (32 Bit): https://dl.dropbox.com/u/60710927/CTR/make_banner/make_banner_1.0_linux.7z

/******** Usage Examples ********/

"make_banner --bnr -g Project/graphics.cbmd -a Project/audio.bcwav -o Project/banner.bnr"

"make_banner --icn -b Project/project.bsf -s project/24x24.ctpk -l project/48x48.ctpk -o project/icon.icn"

/******** Testing 'make_banner' ********/

In directory 'Project' are stock standard input files. They can be used to generate working output.
If you don't have a means to test the output on a 3DS, the output can be checked with 3DSExplorer.

/******** Creating Input Files ********/

Check the Banner Specification File (.BSF) comments for customising the BSF file.(The BSF file is a YAML file, which can be viewed and edited
in a text editor.

